				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One note, though: you should NOT poll $2002 to wait for VBLANK within your game logic, as you'll have a 14% chance of entirely missing the frame due to a timing glitch - if you read $2002 just as VBLANK starts (either on the exact cycle or on the previous cycle), you will read it as being clear but it will actually be set; it will then be cleared, and you will effectively miss the frame. You should use NMI in your game code, even if it does nothing more than set a variable, since it <strong>always</strong> triggers (when enabled).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
